Charles Dunlap (nke ímé yá banyere n'abalị iri abụọ na atọ n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 1983) bụ onye amaara nke ọma site na aha ya bụ Dunlap Exclusive
Ọ bụ Grammy, Stellar na 3x Dove award na-emeri onye na-emepụta egwu si Nashville, Tennessee onye ya na ndị na-ese ihe dịka 2 Chainz, Lloyd, Jim Jones, Trina, Rick Ross na Lecrae rụkọrọ ọrụ.
Dị ka onye ọhụụ, Dunlap chọpụtara na ọ gafeela obodo ya wee kwaga Atlanta ịchụso egwu
Ozugbo ọ na-arụ ọrụ ya, ya na Gorrila Zoe rụkọrọ ọrụ na Block ENT n'ahịa Mixtape
Ógè e mesịrị, ya na Atlanta Def Jam / DTP na-edekọ egwu Playaz Circle rụkọrọ ọrụ yana itinye aka na Tampa's Atlantic / Big Gates nka Plies na abọm ya Goon Affiliated
Dunlap hapụrụ Atlanta ka ya na ndị otu Interscope I Square, na Dirty Money rụọ ọrụ nke ọma na abọm ha "Last Train To Paris" na Los Angeles

Ógè ọ laghachiri Atlanta ntakiri ihe karịrị otu afọ ka e mesịrị, ọ nwetara ebe ọ nọrọ na abọm Jim Jones ' "Capo'. Site n'ebe ahụ, ọ gara n'ihu na-arụ ọrụ na ndị dị ka Lecrae, TLC, Snoop Dogg na ndị ọzọ
Ọ bi ugbu a na Los Angeles, CA
